      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SILVERTREE BRAD (1) filled the minor placings again last time when second (18.51) at this track, making it three straight minors on end. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Has the inside draw and looks tough to beat. BABETTE FUSION (2) has been out of the placings last two but shapes well for this if she can recapture her speedy win a few runs back, getting around this track over 320m in 18.26. Should be in this for a long way. ELECTRIC BLUE (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with five wins and seven minors from 15 tries. Comes off a (18.02) win last time, scoring by 5.5 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 320m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. WICKED RAVEN (8) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when third (18.54) in a Grade 5 over 320m at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide.",
